Package javax.jmdns.impl.tasks.state

Class Summary
Announcer The Announcer sends an accumulated query of all announces, and advances the state of all serviceInfos, for which it has sent an announce.
Canceler The Canceler sends two announces with TTL=0 for the specified services.
DNSStateTask This is the root class for all state tasks.
Prober The Prober sends three consecutive probes for all service infos that needs probing as well as for the host name.
Renewer The Renewer is there to send renewal announcement when the record expire for ours infos.
